I have added some grip tape to both the grip and the slide which is really helpful when your hands sweat. I have also replaced the guide rod and recoil spring. I have a heavier rod and a stiffer spring, both which decrease the amount of felt recoil. Last but not least, I have installed a Powder River Precision Match trigger kit.
